long_description: Built from heavy-gauge steel with a speckled enamel finish, the GSI Pioneer table set delivers classic beauty that will last for years to come. Twelve-piece set includes four 10.5 in. plates, four 5.75 in. bowls and four 12 fl. oz. cups. Every piece has been kiln-hardened twice at 1,400degF for exceptional resistance to scratches and chipping. Three-ply construction maximizes heat distribution.
